        "authorId" : "91d7919c-02c4-40e4-8f30-7f297efebb01",
        "body" : "We should make sure that the expander can not be clicked when the notes editor is being shown. In the current implementation, if we close the expander, the state in the `NoteEditorView` will be lost since we are unmounting that component.\r\n\r\nLikewise, we should make sure that any route changes are protected with a Prompt. I believe you can do this with this component. https://reacttraining.com/react-router/core/api/Prompt",
